<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the function encode() in the class Zend_Pdf_Filter_Compression_Flate there is a problem with the usage of an uninitialized variable in line 54. The line looks like this:</p>

<p>throw new Zend_Pdf_Exception($php_errormsg);</p>

<p>The variable $php_errormsg has not been initialized in the context of the function encode() nor was it passed to the function as a parameter.</p>

